title: Bon Jovi - Milton Keynes (Deluxe Live 2-CD) 1993 ak320
description:
Bon Jovi - Milton Keynes(Deluxe Live 2-CD) 1993 ak320

The I'll Sleep When I'm Dead Tour was a concert tour by American hard rock band Bon Jovi that ran during the second half of 1993. The tour was an extension of the Keep the Faith Tour which was in promotion of the 1992 multi-platinum album Keep the Faith. The tour returned to Europe, Asia and North America.
As is normal with Bon Jovi set lists change regularly and on the second night an extra 4 song encore was played.... Bon Jovi are so consistent live that I have never seen a bad show. Old time pros in 1993 after being together a decade and coming through the aftermath of the Slippery / Jersey mammoth success
